{
  "stem": "3973.5",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And finally, I left my box.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Even though for some years, I would sort of go out into the real world, but I always came back.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Finally, I went back, and I stopped running.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My wife is discouraged, because she has seen me come out before, then I went back again.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now, at this point, I'm convinced.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because it's been holding for a long time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And all of the things which are associated with living in the box and running, all the symptoms of this are gone.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The primary reason why this is working now-- I mean, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There are several things.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "For one, thing it's a question of the time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I have retired last year.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Work was very important to me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was my source of my self-esteem, source of my self-worth and all that.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And when I retired, I thought I couldn't live without it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I found out not only I can do very well without it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But I began to devote a lot of my time, most of my time to working on myself, the true-- my identity.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's not necessarily for now.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I began to grow up.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "For the past 50 odd years, I consider myself to be 14.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I never moved an inch beyond 14 emotionally.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Now, this is as real a statement as can be made.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I not only be-- I acted.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I had some bizarre behavior, which was maybe normal for a 14 year old, but not for 30, 40, or 50 or 60 year old.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But I was stuck in one place emotionally.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I'm beginning to grow up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And it's a wonderful feeling.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But this type of child that I was-- I mean, I was an adult, too.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
